---
title: Chipotle Seitan Chili with Bell Pepper, Cheddar, and Jasmine Rice
description: Seitan, a wheat-based Japanese protein, lends heartiness to this classic chili. A touch of smoky chipotle gives this dish an extra kick. Finished with gooey cheddar, this is vegetarian comfort food at its finest
